title: Which Election Races Are Still Being Called, and When Will We Have Results?
description: Who will control the Senate and the House? Settle in for a long wait.
dc:creator: Nate Cohn
media:credit: Nicole Craine for The New York Times
media:description: As happened in the 2020 election, control of the Senate may come down to a Georgia runoff. Senator Raphael Warnock spoke to supporters in Atlanta after climbing into a narrow lead against Herschel Walker.
